data.description: Beautiful corner lot Sea Country home with one-car garage and one open parking space minutes from community pool and convenience store. Rich dark cabinets in kitchen. Enjoy everything the west side has to offer: World-class beaches and surfing spots, Disney Aulani and Ko'Olina lagoons. Kapolei Commons has movie theaters, Target, Ross's and many eateries. This property is VA approved and loan may be assumed by VA buyer with lender approval. Easy maintenance cement yard perfect for entertaining. Fenced yard great for pets. Laminate flooring throughout the living room and kitchen make for easy living. Central A/C keeps the  home nice and cool. Recessed lights in living room offer warm ambiance. Some furniture and TVs negotiable. Minutes from Pillbox hiking trail. One car garage and one open parking on side of home. (VA assumable loan estimated monthly mortage P and I are $2500.)
